Package: WorkflowRender
Type: Package
Title: Compose and Execute Modular Data Analysis Workflows
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-07-21
Author: xieguigang
Maintainer: xieguigang <xie.guigang@gcmodeller.org>
Description: A helper package for creating and executing modular data
    analysis workflows. WorkflowRender allows users to compose a data
    analysis pipeline from individual application modules, register
    them into a shared workflow context, declare inter-module
    dependencies (both environment symbols and workspace files), and
    execute the pipeline in the correct order with automatic
    dependency validation, performance profiling and structured
    logging. The package also provides utilities for inspecting the
    registered modules, toggling module activation at runtime,
    overriding the execution sequence for debugging, and analyzing
    the dependency graph of the workflow for circular references or
    missing producers.
